BT 1 0 0 1 0 58 Tm /F1 10 Tf 17 TL .923529 Tw (Two or more layers of hatching at different angles. The first layer builds the base value; subsequent layers) Tj T* 0 Tw .923571 Tw (darken specific areas and add textural complexity. Cross-hatching is powerful for deep shadows and rough) Tj T* 0 Tw .353077 Tw (surfaces. The angle between layers affects character: 45-degree crossings feel geometric; gentle curves feel) Tj T* 0 Tw (organic.) Tj T* ET
